In a message dated 2/19/03 12:59:14 AM Central Standard Time, 
airly2002@... writes:


> "Carefull"laughed Hydras while he looked at Maxima"Be carefull, Little 
> Maxima... Couriosity killed the cat... I guess my brave Maxima that you 
> aren't willing a lot to come back to those loosers"

She grinned her sharp toothy grin. "Curiousity hasn't terminated this feline 
yet. & never will."

"As to returning to the base. I would be a fool to return so quickly." Her 
voice dropped to a softer volume & tone. "I would rather go to the Ark or the 
crashed Decepticon vessel than return there." she hated to say that, but it 
was more to get a point across. Of course, it was an excuse to stay in his 
presence. She was there to learn more about him anyway... not race off again.
